description	"Zaalbar

Class Summary: 
A low defense, high offense melee weapon user.

Weaponry:
- Pistol (2)
- Fire Grenades (2)
- Heavy Melee

--- Dual Vibroblades
- Defense 1
- Can block lightsabers, cannot block blaster fire
- Slightly increased damage compared to lightsaber

Attributes:
- Runs faster in melee
- Strength (2) (Immune to Push/Pull, no knockback from blasters)
- Blast Armor
- Force Block (3)

Zaalbar was the son of Wookiee Chieftain Freyyr, but had been exiled from his homeworld. Zaalbar was considered in Wookiee culture to be a madclaw, a title of dishonor, as he had attacked his brother Chuundar with his climbing claws, violating a Wookiee code of conduct."

